{"tid":355784,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"個口多咗粒肉","createTime":"2017-08-11T14:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T10:05:25.000Z","uid":64953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"268d7c7cc3a2eec51c76293302f292ec0d6102ff","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"早排出街食野有舊骨插咗入牙肉到<br />\n依家開始好返少少<br />\n但係我舊肉就分開咗兩舊<br />\n即係會有一粒仔既小牙肉連住個本身個牙肉<br />\n可能有小小1999<br />\n但係有冇人明我講乜同知應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e0b6410dae13015214ad30ddc90545ee8e2833","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早排出街食野有舊骨插咗入牙肉到<br />\n依家開始好返少少<br />\n但係我舊肉就分開咗兩舊<br />\n即係會有一粒仔既小牙肉連住個本身個牙肉<br />\n可能有小小1999<br />\n但係有冇人明我講乜同知應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者簡單D講<br />\n有粒牙肉係舊牙肉到分裂咗出來<br />\n有冇巴絲知應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7462657e00163c0603000b96d394cae6dcb67fbc","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8736cece1eb25d1f8ba350fba7ed2397979ba45b","tid":355784,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:40:11.000Z","msg":"係咪上顎臼齒附近d牙肉"},{"pid":"467e4567555adf93da52e9404d351e07b08d50f0","tid":355784,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"我係智慧齒果度都凸左粒牙肉仔出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670c69ed06a06a209642f9dcddca0ec57193f12d","tid":355784,"uid":88495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"我都試過係口入面生過粒肉(唔係牙肉)<br />\n果陣食野唔小心要損左然後發炎開始爛 過幾日佢慢慢好 但好果陣佢就生粒肉出黎<br />\n粒肉時大時細(最大果陣有手指尾指甲咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 同一時係實的的咁一粒肉 一時係個水泡可以咬爆佢流d滑san san野出黎<br />\n粒肉生左都有一年 一路都冇睇醫生冇理佢<br />\n直到前幾日 佢自己消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e440d8b168e50815e919e9c9cc60c715dc570f","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪上顎臼齒附近d牙肉</blockquote><br />\n我係下顎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8877ec37344ed757ba47e3a67947ccbe8184161c","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過係口入面生過粒肉(唔係牙肉)<br />\n果陣食野唔小心要損左然後發炎開始爛 過幾日佢慢慢好 但好果陣佢就生粒肉出黎<br />\n粒肉時大時細(最大果陣有手指尾指甲咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 同一時係實的的咁一粒肉 一時係個水泡可以咬爆佢流d滑san san野出黎<br />\n粒肉生左都有一年 一路都冇睇醫生冇理佢<br />\n直到前幾日 佢自己消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要成年咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa4d3cdcc2675c78c7ac9ddd82d034c1bd66050","tid":355784,"uid":89846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"我個嘴入面都係，一生就生左四年 無甩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1551fa7ebbcdcec202d1e68c57ef1ccbc5cd16e9","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個嘴入面都係，一生就生左四年 無甩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有冇阻住你食野咁??"},{"pid":"0922830af3998a2bd26c58b4253cc361c534e3b0","tid":355784,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪上顎臼齒附近d牙肉</blockquote><br />\n我係下顎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都有類似情況 不過係上顎<br />\n用條脷頂d牙肉好似就黎甩咁<br />\n戈陣驚到仆街但又唔想睇牙醫<br />\n<br />\n之後舊甩甩地既牙肉慢慢鈣化左 變左好似骨刺咁既物體<br />\n一野啪斷佢之後就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4322d05a3b1b17712c656a2246b3ef11a01b0a75","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪上顎臼齒附近d牙肉</blockquote><br />\n我係下顎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都有類似情況 不過係上顎<br />\n用條脷頂d牙肉好似就黎甩咁<br />\n戈陣驚到仆街但又唔想睇牙醫<br />\n<br />\n之後舊甩甩地既牙肉慢慢鈣化左 變左好似骨刺咁既物體<br />\n一野啪斷佢之後就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae69d0abf3d1ef9f69d018db580d8c92205ebcc","tid":355784,"uid":88495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都試過係口入面生過粒肉(唔係牙肉)<br />\n果陣食野唔小心要損左然後發炎開始爛 過幾日佢慢慢好 但好果陣佢就生粒肉出黎<br />\n粒肉時大時細(最大果陣有手指尾指甲咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 同一時係實的的咁一粒肉 一時係個水泡可以咬爆佢流d滑san san野出黎<br />\n粒肉生左都有一年 一路都冇睇醫生冇理佢<br />\n直到前幾日 佢自己消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要成年咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇睇醫生<br />\n有時生到好撚大舊我會忍痛咬爛粒肉 流好多血不過好彩冇流血不止<br />\n有時佢又生到成個水泡咁我就攞針吉爆佢<br />\n通常佢&quot;受左傷&quot;之後會萎縮變細 但過幾日又生到好大舊<br />\n好彩前幾日好返晒<br />\n不過都係建議巴打如果粒肉過幾日都唔消失都係睇睇醫生穩陣d"},{"pid":"eaafc84759ee759327180929fb7c75d7bc4d0161","tid":355784,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}